(218, 83, 'Dasar Teknik Digital', 'Smart Magazine (Majalah Bulanan United Tractors)', 'Samarinda', NULL, 'Indonesia', '2012', 'Maret', 'Lok', 'sed', 'Teknik Digital merupakan bagian dari sistem Mekatronik, dimana secara umum Mectronic merupakan teknologi yang memadukan electrical, electronic & informasi guna perform kendali mekanikal pada suatu machine. \r\n\r\nSistem kontrol pada mesin meliputi input, proses & output yang mana kesemuanya menggunakan informasi dan logika digital.\r\n\r\nFor service mechanics, it is essential to have an understanding of how the machine works when performing troubleshooting tasks, and it is necessary to learn about electrical and electronic technology as a means of mechanical control. Mechatronics is an essential technology in a wide range of machines, including motor vehicles, home appliances, AV equipment, and industrial equipment. (In 1984, Komatsu launched the PC200-3, which was the first commercially available construction machine equipped with a full mechatronic system.)\r\n\r\nFive purposes of using mectronic systems in contruction machinery: Add New Function, Achieve high precision operation, save energy and improve efficiency of operation, and improve safety.\r\n', '83_karyatulis_smartmagazinemajalahbulananunitedtractors_2e7a5077.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-09-29 17:00:00', '2022-09-29 17:00:00'),
(219, 84, 'The Essential of Human Resources Management ', 'Bintang Sembilan Visitama ', 'Banten', NULL, 'Indonesia', '2021', 'April', 'Nas', 'sed', 'Buku ini menjelaskan tentang prinsipprinsip dasar dalam pengelolaan Sumberdaya Manusia. dikupas dan dibahas\r\noleh penulisnya sehingga pembaca dapat secara gamblang memahami makna dan hakikat dari pengelolaan Manajemen\r\nSumberdaya Manusia', '84_karyatulis_bintangsembilanvisitama_6ecbd473.pdf', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-10-29 03:26:34', '2022-10-27 17:00:00'),
