(168, 63, 'Sem', 'Deep Neural Network for Speaker Identification Using Static and Dynamic Prosodic Feature for Spontan', '2021 International Conference on Advanced Computer Science and Information Systems (ICACSIS)', 'Fasilkom UI', 'Depok', NULL, 'Indonesia', '2021', 'Oktober', 'Int', 'tin', 'We try to recognized spoken language using spontaneous and dictated data using Deep Neural Network approach. Prosodic is information about sound related to tone, intonation, pressure, duration, and rhythm of a person\'s pronunciation.\r\n\r\nBukti karya yang dipresentasikan  dapat dilihat di google scholar di alamat https://scholar.google.com/citations?hl=id&user=t7ug-agAAAAJ&view_op=list_works&sortby=pubdate', '63_seminar_2021internationalconferenceonadvancedcomputerscienceandinformationsystemsicacsis_b9f7ea3a.png', 'W.2.5.1., W.2.5.2., W.2.5.3., W.2.5.4.', 4, 16, 12, NULL, 768, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-10-18 05:52:24', '2022-10-17 17:00:00'),
