(292, 90, 'Sem', 'Simulation of Palu IV Bridge Collapse using Near-Fault Ground Motions', '2019 IABSE Congress New York City ', 'IABSE', 'New York ', NULL, 'Amerika', '2019', 'September', 'Int', 'stin', 'The steel box bowstring arch bridge was located at the near-fault regions (within 1,5 km from fault line) that have not been detected during the design. This bridge may have been damaged by the presence of fling-step pulses in the near-fault pulse-type ground motions that increases the damage potential of such ground motions.', '90_seminar_2019iabsecongressnewyorkcity_d482544f.pdf', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-10-16 17:00:00', '2022-10-16 17:00:00'),
